sources.title: The Houses October Built (FOUND FOOTAGE HORRORFILM in full length, Haunted House Movies German)

metadata.Plot: Beneath the fake blood and cheap masks of countless haunted house attractions across the country, there are whispers of truly terrifying alternatives. Looking to find an authentic, blood-curdling good fright for Halloween, five friends set off on a road trip in an RV to track down these underground Haunts. Just when their search seems to reach a dead end, strange and disturbing things start happening and it becomes clear that the Haunt has come to them...
metadata.Writer: Zack Andrews, Bobby Roe, Jason Zada
metadata.Actors: Brandy Schaefer, Zack Andrews, Bobby Roe
